title: Advantrade

creator: ET FINTECH Pte. Ltd
descriptionHtml:
AdvanTrade is an all-in-one trading application offering stocks, forex. energy, commodities, precious metals and more. Advantrade offers the latest trading functions to our users, helping them through various trading requirements & conditions.

Our operations currently cover across 4 continents, including areas of Southeast Asia, South America, Europe to Africa, including Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, Argentina, Ecuador, Spain, Kenya and more.

Advantrade is confident to offer all users a secure, stable, and responsive trading environment, fully supported by experienced financial professionals and tier one technical teams.
Why should you choose Advantrade?
1. Low Spreads
Enjoy a wide range of products, including forex pairs, commodities, indices, stocks and more with some of the lowest spreads on the market. By using AdvanTrade you will never have to pay any fees or commission on your orders.

2. Secure Transactions
Users can rest assured their personal data and capital is secure with Advantrade, as we at AdvanTrade incorporate the latest in security systems and ensure all industry standards are strictly followed.

3. Education package
Increase your knowledge through our comprehensive trading academy, covering all major financial products including forex pairs, precious metals, energies, cryptocurrencies, on topics such as risk management, financial analysis, trading strategies and much more! You can also arrange real time guidance with our trading experts for free!

4. Self adjustable competitive leverage
AdvanTrade offers upto 400x leverage which users can adjust themselves using our user friendly app

5. Market Trading Experts
Many of our expert trading advisors have over 10+ years experience and are always ready to serve you. All Advantraders can reserve 1 on 1 trading and strategy advice anytime!

6. Live streaming
Our trading experts host regular live streaming sessions to answer any trading enquiries and to share their real world trading experiences

7. 24 hours Service Teams
Our customer support team are available anytime around the clock and ready to answer any questions our users may have
8. Flexible payment channel
Advantrade provides various deposit and withdrawal options, so we ensure you have a choice which suits you best, from bank transfers, credit/debits cards to the most efficient cryptocurrencies.

9. Instant Rebate
Advantraders can now also earn instant rebates, increasing potential returns when you, or your referrals use our services, it’s simple the more you trade more, the more you’ll earn!

Other core features on Advantrade
1. Comprehensive charts and technical analysis
Get more market insights through various chart types, 15+ indicators, technical analysis and drawing tools.

2. Economic calendar
Access and track all major macroeconomic events and international finance news 24 hours daily with Advantrade’s easy-to-use economic calendar.

3. Free demo account
Still unsure and want to try us risk free? Sure! Advantrade offers a free demo account which includes 100,000USD worth of virtual funds for you to test our platform in a real environment but risk free.

4. Real time quotations
You will never miss the best trading opportunities by using our real-time quotation!

Enjoy a wide range of products, including forex pairs, commodities, indices, stocks and more with some of the lowest spreads on the market. By using AdvanTrade you will never have to pay any fees or commission on your orders.

2. Secure Transactions
Users can rest assured their personal data and capital is secure with Advantrade, as we at AdvanTrade incorporate the latest in security systems and ensure all industry standards are strictly followed.

3. Education package
Increase your knowledge through our comprehensive trading academy, covering all major financial products including forex pairs, precious metals, energies, cryptocurrencies, on topics such as risk management, financial analysis, trading strategies and much more! You can also arrange real time guidance with our trading experts for free!

4. Self adjustable competitive leverage
AdvanTrade offers upto 400x leverage which users can adjust themselves using our user friendly app

5. Market Trading Experts
Many of our expert trading advisors have over 10+ years experience and are always ready to serve you. All Advantraders can reserve 1 on 1 trading and strategy advice anytime!

6. Live streaming
Our trading experts host regular live streaming sessions to answer any trading enquiries and to share their real world trading experiences

7. 24 hours Service Teams
Our customer support team are available anytime around the clock and ready to answer any questions our users may have
8. Flexible payment channel
Advantrade provides various deposit and withdrawal options, so we ensure you have a choice which suits you best, from bank transfers, credit/debits cards to the most efficient cryptocurrencies.

9. Instant Rebate
Advantraders can now also earn instant rebates, increasing potential returns when you, or your referrals use our services, it’s simple the more you trade more, the more you’ll earn!

Other core features on Advantrade
1. Comprehensive charts and technical analysis
Get more market insights through various chart types, 15+ indicators, technical analysis and drawing tools.

2. Economic calendar
Access and track all major macroeconomic events and international finance news 24 hours daily with Advantrade’s easy-to-use economic calendar.

3. Free demo account
Still unsure and want to try us risk free? Sure! Advantrade offers a free demo account which includes 100,000USD worth of virtual funds for you to test our platform in a real environment but risk free.

4. Real time quotations
You will never miss the best trading opportunities by using our real-time quotation!
